"description" = "Find your perfect ski resort and ideal accommodation - powered by real data, not fake reviews.\n\nSki Resort Finder is the honest ski app: all data comes from verified sources. No fabricated reviews, no fake prices, no hidden costs. Just real, transparent information for your ski trip planning.\n\n100+ SKI RESORTS IN 15 COUNTRIES\nFrom the Alps to Scandinavia, Scotland to North America, Japan, and New Zealand: explore over 100 ski resorts across 15 countries - including Austria, Switzerland, France, Italy, Germany, USA, Canada, Norway, Sweden, Finland, Japan, Slovenia, and more. Detailed info for every resort: slope kilometers, elevation, and resort size.\n\nREAL ACCOMMODATION DATA\nAll accommodations come from OpenStreetMap - one of the world's largest open geodatabases. Hotels, lodges, chalets, and pensions right on the slopes or in the valley. For every property, you see the exact distance to the nearest lift station in meters.\n\nOBJECTIVE RATING SYSTEM (ORS)\nOur unique rating system is based exclusively on 6 measurable criteria:\n- Distance to lift station\n- Historical snow reliability (10 years of data)\n- Resort quality and size\n- Wellness amenities (pool, spa, sauna, jacuzzi)\n- Hotel classification\n- Elevation\nNo subjective opinions. No paid reviews. Just facts.\n\nLIVE WEATHER & 7-DAY FORECAST\nCurrent weather data for every resort via Open-Meteo API: temperature, snowfall, wind speed, and a detailed 7-day forecast. Plan your ski day to perfection.\n\n10 YEARS OF SNOW STATISTICS\nHistorical snow data analysis for every resort. Compare snowfall, snow days, and snow depth trends across 10 winter seasons with interactive charts. Spot trends and find the most snow-reliable resorts.\n\nTOP RANKINGS IN 5 CATEGORIES\nCompare all resorts across 5 ranking categories: Snowfall, Slope Kilometers, Average Elevation, Max Elevation, and Hotel Rating. Full ranking charts for every category.\n\nWELLNESS & SPA FILTERS\nFilter accommodations by real OpenStreetMap data: pool, jacuzzi, spa, and sauna. Perfect for relaxing after a day on the slopes.\n\nINTERACTIVE MAPS\nVisualize hotels and nearby ski lifts on an interactive map. Standard, satellite, and hybrid views available.\n\nDIRECT CONTACT\nContact hotels directly via email, phone, or website - no middlemen or booking platforms. Pre-filled booking inquiries with your travel dates.\n\nFAVORITES\nSave your favorite ski resorts for quick access. Persistent storage survives app restarts.\n\nPRIVACY FIRST\nSki Resort Finder collects no personal data and uses no tracking. No ads. Snow data is cached locally for offline access (24h cache).\n\n8 LANGUAGES\nAvailable in English, German, French, Spanish, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, and Ukrainian.\n\nBUY ONCE, USE FOREVER\nAll features included. No subscription, no ads, no hidden fees. One fair price for an honest app.\n\nDownload Ski Resort Finder now and plan your next ski trip with real data!";
